OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of
OL,6,Fsome heavy and thundery showers this
OL,7,Fevening. Then becoming dry in the
OL,8,Fearly hours with clear periods and
OL,9,Fsome mist and fog patches.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA bright and mostly dry
OL,12,Fstart to the weekend but some showers
OL,13,Fdeveloping in the west in the
OL,14,Fafternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,17,FRemaining warm on Sunday and Monday
OL,18,Fbut with a freshening breeze, plenty
OL,19,Fof bright weather but one or two
OL,20,Fshowers. Dry and bright with lighter
OL,21,Fwinds on Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
